## Sincere Bizarre Shark Game Implementation

### Game Description

Sincere Bizarre Shark is a two-player abstract strategy game. The game is played on a 5x5 square board. Players take turns placing their pieces on the board. The goal is to create a line of five pieces in any direction (horizontally, vertically, or diagonally).

### Initial Implementation

Here's a simplified implementation of the Sincere Bizarre Shark game in Ludax:

```ludax
(game "Sincere Bizarre Shark"
    (players 2)
    (equipment 
        (board (square 5))
    ) 

    (rules 
        (play
            (repeat (P1 P2)
                (place (destination empty))
            )
        )

        (end 
            (if (line 5) (mover win))
            (if (full_board) (draw))    
        )
    )
)
```

### Adding Piece Movement and Capture

Let's add rules for piece movement and capture. In this version, pieces can move to adjacent empty squares, and capture opponent pieces by jumping over them to an empty square.

```ludax
(game "Sincere Bizarre Shark"
    (players 2)
    (equipment 
        (board (square 5))
    ) 

    (rules 
        (play
            (repeat (P1 P2)
                (place (destination empty))
                (place 
                    (destination 
                        (and 
                            empty 
                            (adjacent (occupied opponent))
                        )
                    )
                    (effects 
                        (capture (adjacent (occupied opponent)))
                    )
                )
            )
        )

        (end 
            (if (line 5) (mover win))
            (if (full_board) (draw))    
        )
    )
)
```

### Adding Shark Piece

Let's introduce a special "Shark" piece that can move and capture in any direction.

```ludax
(game "Sincere Bizarre Shark"
    (players 2)
    (equipment 
        (board (square 5))
    ) 

    (rules 
        (start
            (place P1 (center))
        )
        (play
            (repeat (P1 P2)
                (place (destination empty))
                (place 
                    (destination 
                        (and 
                            empty 
                            (adjacent (occupied opponent))
                        )
                    )
                    (effects 
                        (capture (adjacent (occupied opponent)))
                    )
                )
                (place 
                    (destination 
                        (and 
                            empty 
                            (or 
                                (adjacent (occupied mover))
                                (adjacent (occupied opponent))
                            )
                        )
                    )
                    (mover_is P1)
                )
            )
        )

        (end 
            (if (line 5) (mover win))
            (if (full_board) (draw))    
        )
    )
)
```

### Final Implementation

Here's the final implementation with all the rules:

```ludax
(game "Sincere Bizarre Shark"
    (players 2)
    (equipment 
        (board (square 5))
    ) 

    (rules 
        (start
            (place P1 (center))
        )
        (play
            (repeat (P1 P2)
                (place (destination empty))
                (place 
                    (destination 
                        (and 
                            empty 
                            (adjacent (occupied opponent))
                        )
                    )
                    (effects 
                        (capture (adjacent (occupied opponent)))
                    )
                )
                (place 
                    (destination 
                        (and 
                            empty 
                            (or 
                                (adjacent (occupied mover))
                                (adjacent (occupied opponent))
                            )
                        )
                    )
                    (mover_is P1)
                )
            )
        )

        (end 
            (if (line 5) (mover win))
            (if (full_board) (draw))    
        )
    )
    (rendering
        (color P1 black)
        (color P2 white)
    )
)
```

